rows.text: Chris begins setting up a raffle for a new television set, but Kel ends up breaking it. At the same time, Kenan's parents buy a high-quality TV for themselves, so Kenan plots to somehow replace his parents' TV with the one that Kel broke and then rig the raffle so that Kel wins. Absent: Vanessa Baden as Kyra Rockmore
